com.upsight.android.analytics.session

Interface UpsightSessionCallbacks


  • public interface UpsightSessionCallbacks
    This interface is optionally implemented. Implementations must be referred to in the Android Manifest as meta-data with android:name="com.upsight.session_callbacks" to provide a place to set any configurations before any events get recorded. The #onStart(com.upsight.android.UpsightContext) callback is synchronous and fast-returning. You may only register one implementation of UpsightSessionCallbacks

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onStart(UpsightContext upsight)
      Provides a hook for publishers to be notified when a session is about to start.
